They may have radiation sickness. 

562
00:34:13,240 --> 00:34:16,390
We need to bring them here get them 
to the clinic before it's too late. 

563
00:34:16,830 --> 00:34:17,590
Turn it back on ! 

564
00:34:17,630 --> 00:34:18,700
We've seen it. 

565
00:34:18,720 --> 00:34:20,170
We've seen it 100 timeS. 

566
00:34:20,200 --> 00:34:21,710
A man just died in our clinic. 

567
00:34:21,730 --> 00:34:23,760
Our clinic ! 

568
00:34:24,790 --> 00:34:30,650
He was traveling with his daughter 
and about 20 other people. 

569
00:34:31,100 --> 00:34:38,040
All right,it could have been 
shep or gray or any of us. 

570
00:34:38,730 --> 00:34:40,560
They need our help. 

571
00:34:40,600 --> 00:34:42,940
Are we going to help them ? 

572
00:34:43,040 --> 00:34:49,090
Or are we just going to sit here watching 
the same three images over and over ? 

573
00:34:59,850 --> 00:35:01,510
Jake ? 

574
00:35:01,950 --> 00:35:05,290
I'll donate gas if you need 
to fill your car to get them. 

575
00:35:05,340 --> 00:35:06,160
Thank you,mary. 

576
00:35:06,190 --> 00:35:08,050
I'll go with you. 

577
00:35:09,150 --> 00:35:11,020
Thank you. 

578
00:35:12,650 --> 00:35:14,780
Anybody else ? 

579
00:35:15,480 --> 00:35:16,720
I'll go with you,jake. 

580
00:35:16,750 --> 00:35:18,230
I'll go. 
Let's go. 

581
00:35:18,490 --> 00:35:19,830
Yeah,me,too. 

582
00:35:19,930 --> 00:35:20,910
Thank you. 

583
00:36:05,810 --> 00:36:10,720
Earlier today,we buried 20 people...
refugees from denver. 

584
00:36:10,770 --> 00:36:18,030
People we didn't know,but were 
prepared to welcome into our town. 

585
00:36:18,060 --> 00:36:23,000
Unfortunately,they died of radiation 
poisoning before we could reach them. 

586
00:36:23,820 --> 00:36:31,700
For those people from denver,and for our 
own people,for sheriff dawes and deputy riley,

587
00:36:31,750 --> 00:36:35,280
for deputy conner and deputy salem...

588
00:36:37,750 --> 00:36:44,500
for eople out there somewhere we know nothing 
about who might be suffering and dying right now...

589
00:36:44,530 --> 00:36:48,530
I ask that we take a moment of silence. 

590
00:36:53,570 --> 00:36:58,050
If you've lost a loved one,would you please stand ? 

591
00:37:04,980 --> 00:37:10,780
If someone you love is missing,
would you join those standing ? 

592
00:37:20,950 --> 00:37:28,240
We stand because we know that every life matters. 

593
00:37:28,960 --> 00:37:33,360
We have to fight for every life,

594
00:37:33,390 --> 00:37:40,270
even when it seems hopeless,even when we're afraid,

595
00:37:40,780 --> 00:37:46,990
because the battle ahead isn't just for our survival,

596
00:37:49,840 --> 00:37:53,510
it's for our humanity. 

597
00:38:15,130 --> 00:38:17,530
I think I'm going to be okay. 

598
00:38:19,700 --> 00:38:20,890
Jake. 

599
00:38:21,330 --> 00:38:22,620
Hi. 

